ownedNfts.name: Crypto Boy #18
ownedNfts.description:
“Crypto ₿oy” is a wake-up call for all the chart-watchers, candle-counters, and JPEG-flippers that find a way to bring crypto into any conversation, no matter what it’s about.

We all know them — checking OpenSea like it’s instagram, obsessing over prices, hodling this, shorting that and unable to focus on anything except Discord.

As exciting as crypto is, and as likely as it is to revolutionize finance in the coming years, I want to shift our attention to a very urgent issue, which is the possibility of SCOTUS overturning Roe v Wade. This attack on reproductive rights is something we should be talking about as loudly as a crypto boy talks about NFTs*. It’s imperative that we band together and fight to protect our fundamental rights. To help bring this together I partnered with Nadya Tolokonnikova of Pussy Riot, who I love and respect, to create the custom art for this NFT.

100% of the proceeds of the sale of this NFT will be donated to The Center for Reproductive Rights (https://reproductiverights.org), a legal nonprofit that is able to accept donations in cryptocurrency.

ownedNfts.name: Fuck Around and Find Out #34
ownedNfts.description:
The iconic 'F*ck Around and Find Out' meme by Roger Skaer, was first uploaded as a TikTok video on September 27th, 2022. This relatable comedy short quickly became a viral sensation, gathering millions of views, likes, and shares on TikTok, Twitter and other social media platforms in its first few days, forever securing its meme-worthy place in internet history and culture.

The meme quickly caught the eye of notable personalities like Elon Musk, who quoted it on Twitter with the acronym “FAFO”. It even found its way into Afrojack's incredible live music set at the Ultra Music Festival in Miami, on screen and remixed in front of thousands of music fans, gaining millions more views on Youtube as well.

Roger's iconic video has not only entertained millions over social media and television but also opened doors to exciting collaborations. Paving the way for partnerships with influential institutions such as the NFL, ESPN, and more celebrities using video and the ‘F*ck Around and Find Out’ quote. With each passing day, its cultural significance continues to grow as one of the most used modern memes!

Roger Skaer has partnered exclusively with Melon to turn his original Tiktok video, the meme itself, into a collectible NFT drop. Come F*ck Around and Find Out what it means to truly own a piece of internet history.

Paying homage to the projects and 1/1 artists that inspired me throughout 2022 in this action-packed class photo.

In a year where it seemed that we were all struggling to survive in a difficult market, I wanted to create something that would serve as a reminder of the passion and drive that brought us all here. This piece is a celebration of the enduring power of art to uplift and inspire us, even in the darkest of times. 

The best way I can show love and say thank you is through my art. Happy 2023.

We don’t know

But our purest intentions will remain as foundations for things to come while former frenzies fade like tulips made out of ashes

We are just getting started

ownedNfts.name: Forge the Memes
ownedNfts.description:
The Zestaphoni Ferroalloy Plant, a metallurgical factory that was established in 1933 during the Soviet era, is located in the country of Georgia and has been in operation 24/7 ever since. The plant's heating furnaces need to remain active at all times, necessitating continuous monitoring by the workers. Some of the employees have been working at the company 'GM' (Georgian Manganese) for over 40 years, observing firsthand the evolution of industrial society as they help create the alloys that power it.  
  
Koopmans traveled to Georgia with a camera and captured this forging of the memes.       
  
Meme: 1  
Season: 3  
Card: 1

ownedNfts.name: Seized by Seduction
ownedNfts.description:
Passion and seduction are powerful forces that can drive us to pursue our desires and dreams with a relentless determination. When we are truly passionate about something, we become fully immersed in it, and our enthusiasm can be contagious, inspiring others to join us in our quest.   
   
Similarly, seduction can be a potent tool for persuading others to follow our lead, drawing them in with our charm and charisma. However, the key to sustaining this drive is to never become complacent, to always strive for more and never settle for less. To keep up with the ever-evolving world around us, we must be willing to adapt and grow, continually pushing ourselves to new heights.    
   
See… WAGMI.

ownedNfts.name: God Save The Key
ownedNfts.description:
“God Save The Key” by artist YuYu takes a spin on renaissance masterpieces to humourlessly remind us the importance of self sovereignty - Not your Keys, Not your coins. YuYu's reinterpretation of Jacques-Louis David's painting The Oath of the Horatii (1786) draws inspiration from the three depicted brothers and their unity, reflecting the collective efforts of the web3 community to defend and uphold its ethos.   
   
Additionally, the artwork combines elements from Karl Brullov's The Last Day of Pompeii (1833), lighting with its eruption the left corner of the background, and Briton Riviere's lions from Daniel's Answer to the King (1892) encircle the main character, serving as indicators of imminent danger. Through these conceptual elements, the work depicts the turbulent nature of cryptocurrency while emphasizing the vital role of unity and collective action in fortifying decentralization.  
   
Artworks used:   
1. The Oath of the Horatii 1786 - Jacques-Louis David   
2. The Last Day of Pompeii 1833 - Karl Brullov   
3. Daniel's Answer To The King 1892 - Briton Riviere   
  
Meme: 10  
Season: 3  
Card: 1

ownedNfts.description:
Yesterday, dawn arose, morning's haunting grace.   
Time stood still, night revealed its face.   
Those present yesterday, might not be here tomorrow,   
Echoes of them linger, evoking hope and sorrow.   
The Green remains silent, unaware what lies behind.   
Doors keep their secrets, hidden from our eyes.   
It doesn't choose the hour, nor is it bound by place,   
Transcending softly, traversing time and space.

ownedNfts.name: Equilibrium
ownedNfts.description:
In the heart of the abyss stands a monolith-like structure, representing a scale, a balance between both worlds with its "weights" extending on both sides.   
   
The left side, a vibrant depiction of nature unfolds, captivating the essence of real-life experiences and fundamental rights, evoking a connection to our physical world.   
   
The right side of the scale however, takes on a digital persona. This realm represents the realm of Digital Rights, where the virtual realm intertwines with our daily lives.   
   
We witness the delicate balance between real-world and digital rights, where one cannot exist without the other, emphasizing the imperative to value each sphere equally. A profound reminder that compromising either realm would undermine the harmonious coexistence of these vital aspects of our lives.   
   
TLDR; SEIZE THE RIGHTS OF DIGITALIZATION

Season: 4
